<div id="how" class="page-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="text-center">Simple Steps</h2>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
        <p >Sign in with facebook, choose a major/Industry that you are pursuing</p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
        <p>Enter what you are currently learning or what you want to learn, You will be suggested users that are learning the same</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
         <p>Follow suggested users or find users to follow and see what resources they are using and what they are sharing</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
           <p>Find/create groups that are related to your learning goals</p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
          <p> You can start sharing the resources that you use or what you are learning and people who follow can see it and give you feedback </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-xs-12 col-xs-12">
           <p>Ask questions other like minded people in groups or in questions/answers tab to allow everyone in your industry to see it in their feed</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row text-center">
        <span class="how-it-works-btn">
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-success btn-large"> Get Started </a>
      </span>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<div id="members" class="page-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="text-center">Most recent members</h2>
    <div class="most-recent row">

      <% @recent_memebers.each do |user| %>
      <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3">
        <div class="pull-left user-slider">
          <div class="useravatar text-center"><%= image_tag user.avatar.url(:thumb), :class => "img-circle"%></div>
          <ul>
            <li><a class="user-name" href="/users"><%= user.first_name %> <%=user.last_name %></a></li>
            <li><%= user.location%>
            <li>
              <a class="btn btn-success btn-large" href="/users/sign_up">Follow</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
       <%end%>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

